UMnuz Patrick Lipudi (59) kuthiwa ushone izolo ekuseni emuva kokuba engeniswe esibhedlela iHelen Joseph ngoMgqibelo. Ngokwemibiko yabezindaba, isikhulu kulo masipala ehhovisini lemeya uMnuz Sabelo Ngwane sikuqinisekisile ukudlula emhlabeni kwalo mholi. UNgwane uthe umndeni usashaqekile ngokudlula ngokuzuma kukaLipudi obengubaba aphinde abe yinsika yekhaya. ULipudi ube yimeya kulo masipala ngo-2017 ngesikhathi i-ANC iwubuyisa kwiDA kanti phambilini ubenguSomlomo.